caption%3ETyra%20Banks%20sold%20her%20Hot%20Mama%20%26quot%3Bhot%20ice%20cream%26quot%3B%20at%20her%20ice%20cream%20shop%20in%20Sydney.%3Cp%3ESmize%20%26amp%3B%20Dream%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c8d5a52-80a7-4d97-b98d-025a791ac3aa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Ice%20cream%20reimagined'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Smize%20%26amp%3B%20Dream%20team%20said%20Hot%20Mama%20isn't%20melted%20ice%20cream.%20It's%20also%2C%20they%20said%2C%20not%20hot%20chocolate%20nor%20a%20latte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20ice%20cream%20reimagined%20%E2%80%94%20churned%2C%20simmered%2C%20and%20perfected%20to%20be%20served%20warm%20and%20sippable%2C%20poured%20into%20a%20couture%203D%20cup%2C%20and%20finished%20with%20signature%20SMiZE%20flair%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20describes%20Hot%20Mama%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20liquid%20version%20of%20your%20favorite%20ice%20cream%20scoop%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Ba%20culinary%20contradiction%20that%20shouldn't%20make%20sense%2C%20but%20somehow%2C%20deliciously%20does.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20if%20that%20only%20led%20to%20more%20questions%20than%20answers%2C%20Banks%20also%20shared%20insights%20into%20how%20she%20and%20the%20Smize%20%26amp%3B%20Dream%20team%20developed%20hot%20ice%20cream.%20They%20said%20they%20spent%20over%20a%20year%20testing%20texture%2C%20formulation%2C%20and%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20first%2C%20we%20tried%20just%20heating%20standard%20ice%20cream%20bases%2C%20but%20they%20turned%20sticky%2C%20gloopy%2C%20or%20too%20thin%2C%26quot%3B%20Banks%20said%20in%20the%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BThe%20breakthrough%20came%20when%20we%20found%20the%20perfect%20viscosity%20%E2%80%94%20not%20too%20thick%2C%20not%20too%20thin%20%E2%80%94%20where%20hot%20ice%20cream%20still%20felt%20as%20dreamy%20as%20cold%20ice%20cream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%2C%20the%20Smize%20%26amp