plays%2C%26quot%3B%20Luckey%20told%20reporters%20at%20a%20press%20briefing%20on%20October%208.%20%26quot%3BMy%20investors%20at%20the%20time%20told%20me%20that%20I%20could%20not%20put%20all%20our%20eggs%20in%20that%20basket%20because%20they%20believed%20it%20was%20an%20extension%20of%20a%20pissing%20contest%20I%20had%20with%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20as%20to%20how%20to%20build%20the%20best%20augmented%20reality%20glasses.%20They%20were%20somewhat%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20contributing%20the%20%26quot%3Bwaveguide%20and%20display%20technology%26quot%3B%20to%20EagleEye%2C%20Luckey%20said.%20The%20partnership%20has%20also%20afforded%20Luckey%20access%20to%20Meta's%20virtual%20reality%20intellectual%20property%2C%20some%20of%20which%20Luckey%20himself%20developed%20at%20Oculus.%20%26quot%3BI%20now%20have%20all%20my%20toys%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20that%20I%20did%20before%20I%20sold%20the%20company%2C%20everything%20I%20did%20while%20I%20was%20at%20Meta%2C%20and%20everything%20that%20they%20did%20afterward%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20it%20is%20on%20the%20table%20for%20EagleEye.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckey%20also%20added%20that%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20this%20part%20of%20Meta's%20tech%20is%20%26quot%3Boutside%20of%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20US-based%2C%26quot%3B%20although%20he%20wouldn't%20elaborate%20on%20the%20specific%20location.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20quite%20aligned%20with%20the%20US%20military%20goals%20of%20not%20being%20dependent%20on%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Anduril%2C%20Microsoft%20was%20working%20on%20military%20smart%20goggles%2C%20but%2C%20in%20February%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anduril.com%2Farticle%2Fanduril-and-microsoft-partner-to-advance-integrated-visual-augmentation-system-ivas-program-for%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehanded%20over%20the%20Integrated%20Visual%20Augmentation%20System