sla%20manufactures%20its%20cars%20for%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUS%20market%20in%20its%20Fremont%20Factory%20in%20California%20and%20Gigafactory%20Texas%2C%20where%20land%2C%20labor%2C%20and%20permits%20are%20already%20costly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20slapped%20not%20just%20a%20large%20tariff%2C%20but%20a%20large%20and%20uncertain%20tariff%20on%20that%20type%20of%20trade%2C%20it%20is%20really%20hard%20to%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Fisher.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20in%20the%20car%20business%2C%20thinking%20about%20building%20an%20EV%20or%20a%20hybrid%20and%20installing%20a%20bunch%20of%20batteries%20in%20the%20vehicle%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20what%20I%20would%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad0ab14b-4be5-4b97-9fc2-a3856f5d24f3%5C%22%3ETrump's%20EV%20policies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20add%20to%20Tesla's%20pricing%20woes%2C%20the%20US%20is%20moving%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%20in%20terms%20of%20EV%20policy%20compared%20to%20other%20major%20EV%20markets%20worldwide%2C%20especially%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20to%20suspend%20all%20disbursements%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-reduction-act-how-it-reduces-price-growth-deficit-pressures-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20funding%2C%20a%20Biden-era%20package%20passed%20by%20Congress%20that%20aims%20to%20boost%20clean%20energy%20production%20and%20job%20creation%20in%20rural%20America.%20The%20set%20of%20119%20provisions%20includes%20up%20to%20%247%2C500%20in%20tax%20credit%20for%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enew%20EV%20buyers%2C%20credits%20for%20businesses%20purchasing%20commercial%20clean%20vehicles%2C%20and%20funding%20to%20build%20more%20charging%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20ordered%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20steps%26quot%3B%20to%20reinstate%20IRA%20funding%20that%20had%20already%20been%20awarded%20to%20projects.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20Congress%20and%20signed%20into%20law%20by%20Trump%2C%20still%20eliminated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-tax-credit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEV%20tax%20credits%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20all%20vehicles%20purchased%20after%20September%2030.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Tesla's%20new%20cheaper%20models%20are%20still%20around%20%242%2C000%20more%20expensive%20than%20what%20the%20flagship%20versions%20would%20have%20cost%20had%20the%20%247%2C500%20EV%20credit%20remained%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20also%20used%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20an%20income%20by%20selling%20clean%20vehicle%20credits%20to%20combustion%20engine%20vehicle%20manufacturers%20that%20fail%20to%20meet%20emission%20standards%2C%20until%20Trump%20eliminated%20the%20fines%20on%20those%20automakers%2C%20which%20Fisher%20said%20may%20be%20limiting%20Tesla's%20financial%20ability%20to%20comfortably%20make%20a%20larger%20price%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229202d734-33a5-4c8e-af51-921ad9ed5ccb%5C%22%3EHow%20China%20has%20managed%20to%20make%20cheaper%20EVs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20models%20of%20BYD%2C%20a%20Chinese%20Tesla%20competitor%2C%20are%20selling%20in%20China%20for%20the%20equivalent%20of%20around%20%2420%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20China%2C%20it%20has%20the%20advantage%20of%20labor%2C%20and%20it%20is%20not%20as%20strict%20on%20environmental%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Fisher.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20in%20terms%20of%20permitting%20and%20just%20getting%20things%20done%2C%20every%20permit%20is%20way%20harder%20to%20obtain%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20even%20if%20you%20do%2C%20there%20is%20a%20good%20chance%20you%20would%20get%20sued%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20another%20factor.%20According%20to%20the%20Rhodium%20Group%2C%20China's%20governm