Manhattan%20federal%20court%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20convicted%20of%20the%20conspiracy%2C%20wire%20fraud%2C%20and%20money%20laundering%20charges%20against%20them%2C%20the%20brothers%20%E2%80%94%20both%20highly%20educated%20in%20math%20and%20computer%20sciences%20%E2%80%94%20face%20a%20maximum%20sentence%20of%2020%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20each%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20comes%20amid%20efforts%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20bring%20more%20order%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-crypto-reserve-bitcoin-btc-eth-prices-coins-rally-questions-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecryptocurrency%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20through%20new%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22383c0548-0068-47e8-a207-764030a85afd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20prosecutors'%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20the%20pair's%2012-second%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fethereum-vs-bitcoin-eth-btc-price-crypto-rally-spot-etfs-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEthereum%20blockchain%3C%2Fa%3E%20theft%20in%20April%202023%20was%20%26quot%3Bmeticulously%20planned%26quot%3B%20over%20at%20least%20three%20months%2C%20right%20down%20to%20their%20online%20searches%20for%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20wash%20crypto%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btop%20crypto%20lawyers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%20launder%20%3Cem%3Estatue%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20limitations%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20say%20they%20searched%20at%20one%20point%2C%20misspelling%20statute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%2C%20prosecutors%20allege%2C%20used%20%26quot%3Bbait%20transactions%26quot%3B%20to%20find%20three%20victim%20traders%20and%20study%20their%20trading%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20%26quot%3Blured%26quot%3B%20the%20victims'%20trading%20bots%20into%20a%20carefully%20set%2C%20fast-acting%20trap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trap%20was%20set%20with%20an%20irresistible%20bundle%20of%20crypto%20trades%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20of%20transactions%20that%20the%20brothers%20correctly%20guessed%20the%20victim's%20bots%20would%20leap%20at%20the%20chance%20to%20profit%20from%2C%20prosecutors%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20then%20sprung%20the%20trap%20shut.%20Prosecutors%20say%20they%20exploited%20a%20software%20%26quot%3Bvulnerability%26quot%3B%20that%20let%20them%20quickly%20glimpse%20their%20prey's%20private%20transaction%20information%20and%20%26quot%3Btamper%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20purchase%20in%20a%20classic%20bait-and-switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20generating%20an%20anticipated%20windfall%2C%20the%20victims%20found%20that%20their%20%2425%20million%20had%20purchased%20a%20pile%20of%20effectively%20worthless%2C%20illiquid%20junk%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20the%20way%2C%20prosecutors%20say%2C%20the%20brothers%20hid%20their%20own%20identities%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20location%20of%20the%20heist's%20ill-gotten%20gain%20%E2%80%94%20through%20a%20web%20of%20shell%20companies%2C%20crypto%20addresses%2C%20and%20foreign%20crypto%20exchanges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heist%20itself%2C%20prosecutors%20say%2C%20was%20executed%20in%20just%2012%20seconds%20%E2%80%94%20the%20brief%20pause%20between%20the%20moment%20a%20crypto%20trade%20is%20made%20and%20when%20it%20is%20officially%20logged%20on%20the%20blockchain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20the%20specialized%20skills%20developed%20during%20their%20education%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20expertise%20in%20cryptocurrency%20trading%26quot%3B%20the%20brothers%20%26quot%3Bexploited%20the%20very%20integrity%20of%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20said%20in%20a%2019-page%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Peraire-Bueno%20brothers%20%26quot%3Bmanipulated%20and%20tampered%20with%20the%20process%20and%20protocols%20by%20which%20transactions%20are%20validated%20and%20added%20to%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20indictment%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20fraudulently%20gained%20access%20to%20pending%20private%20transactions%20and%20used%20that%20access%20to%20alter%20transactions%20and%20obtain%20their%20victims'%20cryptocurrency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers'%20lawyers%20have%20told%20prosecutors%20that%20they%20are%20not%20interested%20in%20even%20considering%20taking%20a%20plea%2C%20prosecutors%20revealed%20at%20a%20hearing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eafa275e-c62d-468a-babb-689a63347c2e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20backing%20down%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20defense%20is%20set%20to%20push%20back%20hard%20against%20the%20prosecution's%20allegations%2C%20at%20trial%2C%20before%20a%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20central%20authority%26quot%3B%20governing%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%2C%20Patrick%20Looby%2C%20who%20represents%20the%20elder%20brother%2C%20James%2C%20told%20US%20District%20Court%20Judge%20Jessica%20G.%20L%20Clarke%20during%20oral%20arguments%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20there's%20no%20government%20regulations.%20Instead%2C%20economic%20incentives%20guide%20parties'%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20Looby%20argued.%20Prosecutors%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20alleging%20conduct%20that%20the%20government%20has%20never%20sought%20to%20criminalize%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20including%20taking%20advantage%20of%20a%20software%20vulnerability%20or%20using%20a%20crypto%20transaction%20as%20%26quot%3Bbait.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20fraud%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20promise%20to%20the%20victim%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20also%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%2C%20there%20is%20no%20alleged%20communication%20at%20all%20between%20the%20Peraire-Buenos%20and%20the%20traders.%20And%20for%20that%20reason%20as%20well%2C%20there's%20no%20alleged%20intent%20to%20defraud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20so-called%20victims%20%26quot%3Bmade%20very%20risky%20bets%20on%20a%20strategy%20that%20didn't%20pay%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there%20was%20nothing%20stolen%20and%20there%20was%20no%20theft%2C%20as%20that%20word%20would%20normally%20be%20used.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20victims%20lost%20their%20cryptocurrency%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20pre-programmed%20trades%20without%20ever%20interacting%20with%20the%20Peraire-Buenos%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20defense%20attorneys%20argued%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20in%20a%20failed%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20this%20indictment%2C%20no%20Ethereum%20user%20would%20have%20understood%20that%20thwarting%20a%20predatory%20attempt%20by%20'bots'%20engaged%20in%20market%20manipulation%20could%20lead%20to%20criminal%20charges%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20court%20has%20ever%20applied%20these%20statutes%20to%20similar%20transactions%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20argued.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20Peraire-Buenos%20had%20no%20reason%20to%20know%20that%20their%20alleged%20conduct%20may%20be%20considered%20unlawful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20defense%20team%20declined%20Business%20Insider's%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20case.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20prosecution%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProspective%20jurors%20will%20be%20told%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20trial%20may%20run%20into%20the%20first%20week%20of%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-brothers-peraire-bueno-trial-heist-ethereum-blockchain-arguments-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760347801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e6a3aa5dbc4fd10daa7536%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-brothers-peraire-b