hinking%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-small-town-from-big-city-surprising-benefits-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20somewhere%20new%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20somewhere%20near%20my%20mother%20with%20warm%20weather.%20We're%20beach%20people%2C%20so%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-us-from-spain-taught-me-about-work-culture-family-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elanded%20on%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202024%2C%20we%20took%20a%20trip%20there%20to%20experience%20it%20firsthand%20and%20loved%20it%20so%20much%20that%20we%20knew%20it%20was%20right%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fed22dfe-9fa7-414a-b77f-6a8282e3f0eb%5C%22%3EBefore%20moving%20to%20Spain%2C%20we%20went%20on%20a%20road%20trip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20making%20the%20leap%20to%20Spain%2C%20we%20sold%20our%20home%20and%20auctioned%20off%20everything%20in%20it%20%E2%80%94%20furniture%2C%20kitchenware%2C%20and%20all%20the%20little%20knickknacks%20we'd%20accumulated%20over%20the%20years.%20We%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsell-investment-property-stopped-being-landlord-put-money-in-market-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esold%20our%20other%20real-estate%20properties%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20decent%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20decided%20to%20fulfill%20a%20lifelong%20dream%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Five-spent-5-months-traveling-us-rv-with-husband-kids-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraveling%20around%20the%20US%20in%20an%20RV%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20wanted%20to%20test%20if%20I%20could%20take%20my%20business%20on%20the%20road%20and%20reconnect%20as%20a%20family%2C%20knowing%20that%20in%20Spain%2C%20with%20the%20language%20barrier%20and%20a%20brand-new%20environment%2C%20it%20would%20be%20just%20us%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C