2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f74dfcd-37e2-4b39-b301-35448f61135b%5C%22%3ESpain%20isn't%20as%20affordable%20as%20I%20thought%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20surprised%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-arizona-to-spain-for-more-relaxed-life-burnout-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20living%20in%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20significantly%20less%2C%20and%20it's%20really%20not.%20The%20prices%20for%20goods%20and%20services%20have%20gone%20up%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years%20from%20when%20we%20first%20started%20thinking%20about%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20apartment%20costs%20about%20the%20same%20as%20the%20one%20we%20had%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20and%20we're%20spending%20about%20the%20same%20on%20groceries%20as%20we%20did%20in%20the%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Izabela%20Oquendo%20and%20her%20daughter%20walking%20throughout%20a%20Spanish%20town.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e9481c5dbc4fd10daaa49e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOquendo%20and%20her%20daughter%20walking%20about%20town.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Izabela%20Oquendo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20been%20difficult%20to%20communicate%20with%20the%20locals.%20My%20husband%20speaks%20Spanish%2C%20but%20the%20dialect%20here%20is%20different.%20We're%20getting%20by%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20biggest%20fears%20about%20moving%20to%20Spain%20was%20how%20my%20kids%20would%20handle%20learning%20the%20language%20and%20assimilating%20into%20the%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20definitely%20notice%20they're%20in%20a%20new%20country.%20When%20we%20arrived%2C%20we%20enrolled%20them%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Flearning%2Fhow-to-learn-spanish-online-beginner-classes-apps-books%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpanish%20lessons%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20give%20them%20a%20foundation.%20Of%20course%2C%20they're%20still%20learning%20the%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20is%20very%20social%2C%20but%20when%20she%20first%20started%20school%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20for%20her%20to%20make%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she'd%20never%20struggled%20with%20before.%20It's%20because%20she%20can't%20just%20walk%20up%20and%20start%20talking%20to%20them%3B%20the%20other%20kids%20don't%20speak%20the%20same%20language.%20That%20was%20tough%2C%20but%20an%20English-language%20camp%20we%20also%20enrolled%20her%20in%20has%20helped%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20for%20parents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-portugal-greece-cost-of-living-quality-of-life-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20their%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20new%20country%20is%20to%20be%20gentle%20with%20the%20process.%20Kids%20are%20resilient%20and%20adapt%20to%20almost%20anything.%20I%20grew%20up%20with%20immigrant%20parents%2C%20so%20I%20remember%20this%20from%20my%20own%20upbringing.%20I%20think%20if%20you%20provide%20a%20stable%20structure%20and%20show%20up%20consistently%2C%20the%20external%20stuff%20matters%20much%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4a5246c-d455-4c1b-b8de-1f163ee58aad%5C%22%3EMoney%20no%20longer%20defines%20my%20happiness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20things%20we%20wanted%20in%20moving%20to%20Spain%20was%20a%20slower%20life.%20In%20Connecticut%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20constantly%20working%20%E2%80%94%20passing%20each%20other%20during%20the%20day%20and%20collapsing%20at%20night.%20It%20was%20a%20grind%20we%20weren't%20enjoying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20working%20here%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20less.%20I%20continue%20to%20do%20accounting%20and%20bookkeeping%20for%20my%20US%20clients%2C%20and%20am%20transitioning%20into%20more%20healing%20and%20therapeutic%20work.%20In%20June%2C%20I%20published%20a%20